TITLE: Dog Collar and Leash, Tugboat, 6ft leash, 1 inch wide, adjustable, quick release, metal buckle, chain, martingale, hybrid, nylon
DESCRIPTION:
All Caninedesign collars are 1 inch wide and adjustable. Leashes are 6 feet. They are quality, handmade items. Materials are purchased in large bulk quantities to keep costs down. 

In the drop down menu, you can choose type of collar (buckle, metal buckle, martingale, chain, hybrids). Please visit our blog for descriptions of each choice. 
http://caninedesigncollars.blogspot.com/2015/07/pictures-of-collar-types.html

We can also add white, Sherpa fleece padding to any collar or leash handle. Leash handle padding is an additional $5. Please contact us before ordering.

Choose neck size (inches) in the dropdown menu. If you know your dog's exact neck measurement, type that in the notes, and Caninedesign will make a custom fit.

The color nylon shown is the default unless you specify another color in the notes at checkout.
